    <description>Stalingrad is a supplement for Flames of War: The World War II Miniatures Game, the World War II miniatures game. It provides the organization and equipment for the Soviet and German Infantry Forces involved in the battle for Stalingrad.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For the Soviet, there are covers special rules and full stats on the Soviet equipment, guns, vehicles and teams. There are organisation lists for Strelkovy Batalon (Infantry Battalion), Guardeyskiy Strelkovy Batalon (Guard Infantry Battalion) and Batalon Opolecheniya (Militia Battalion). The second two are variations on the Strelkovy Batalon, allowing for either better-trained troops (Guards) or lower motivation (Militia).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The German forces found in this book are the Grenadiers: Grenadierkompanie, Schnellschwadron,  Pionierkompanie and Luftwaffe Feldkompanie.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Street Fighting Rules are also included as well as tactics articles, painting guide, rules for warriors and snipers and new scenarios.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
